[SN]TITLE[SN]
Motorcyclist dies in crash with car

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 26-year-old man has died after his motorbike was involved in a collision with a car in Aberdeenshire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The accident happened shortly before 15:00 on the B977 near Echt.
Three women travelling in the BMW car which was involved in the collision were not injured.
The road was closed while emergency services responded to the incident.
